The paper deals with annotating RGBD images, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) techniques. The system also performs tasks such as grouping pixels and inferring object interactions, which are related to artificial intelligence (AI). The paper also mentions learning from previous annotation sessions, which falls under machine learning (LG). Finally, the paper deals with indoor scenes, which could fall under computer graphics (GR).
